# Windsurf Cascade Project Rules (Shim)
# Legacy compatibility: projects may symlink this file into repo root as .windsurfrules
#   ln -s /opt/fabrik/windsurfrules .windsurfrules

# DEPRECATION NOTICE
# This file is a compatibility shim. Authoritative rules live in:
#   /opt/fabrik/.windsurf/rules/

## Traycer-Managed Override
If a task is Traycer-managed, defer to:
- AGENTS.md
- .windsurf/rules/*

## Canonical Rule Sources (DO NOT DUPLICATE HERE)
- Workspace rules directory (authoritative): /opt/fabrik/.windsurf/rules/
- Global rules (optional, per-user): global_rules.md (Windsurf global)
